<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>NOXAR — IA, Automação e Escala para Empresas Ambiciosas</title>
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="A NOXAR constrói sistemas com IA, automação e infraestrutura digital para empresas que querem escalar com margem, velocidade e previsibilidade."
  />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#08101f" />

  <style>
    :root{
      --bg:#050814;
      --bg-2:#09101f;
      --card:#0f172a;
      --card-2:#111c33;
      --line:rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      --text:#f7f9ff;
      --muted:#a7b3d4;
      --primary:#6c8cff;
      --primary-2:#2ce5c0;
      --danger:#ff6b81;
      --shadow:0 24px 70px rgba(0,0,0,.45);
      --radius:22px;
      --max:1180px;
    }

    *{
      margin:0;
      padding:0;
      box-sizing:border-box;
    }

    html{
      scroll-behavior:smooth;
    }

    body{
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(108,140,255,.18), transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(44,229,192,.10), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #040711 0%, #08101f 100%);
      color:var(--text);
      line-height:1.6;
      overflow-x:hidden;
    }

    a{
      text-decoration:none;
      color:inherit;
    }

    img{
      max-width:100%;
      display:block;
    }

    .container{
      width:min(92%, var(--max));
      margin:0 auto;
    }

    .section{
      padding:84px 0;
    }

    .eyebrow{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:10px;
      padding:8px 14px;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:999px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      color:#dce5ff;
      font-size:.92rem;
      font-weight:700;
      margin-bottom:18px;
    }

    .eyebrow-dot{
      width:10px;
      height:10px;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-2));
      box-shadow:0 0 16px rgba(44,229,192,.85);
    }

    .btn{
      display:inline-flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:center;
      gap:10px;
      border:none;
      cursor:pointer;
      padding:14px 22px;
      border-radius:14px;
      font-weight:800;
      transition:.25s ease;
      font-size:.98rem;
    }

    .btn-primary{
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), #4e69ff);
      color:#fff;
      box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(108,140,255,.32);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover{
      transform:translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow:0 18px 36px rgba(108,140,255,.4);
    }

    .btn-secondary{
      color:#fff;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      backdrop-filter:blur(8px);
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      transform:translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-whatsapp{
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, #16c55f, #0aa84f);
      color:#fff;
      box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(22,197,95,.25);
    }

    .btn-whatsapp:hover{
      transform:translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow:0 18px 36px rgba(22,197,95,.35);
    }

    header{
      position:sticky;
      top:0;
      z-index:100;
      backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
      background:rgba(5,8,20,.72);
      border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.05);
    }

    .nav{
      min-height:80px;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:18px;
    }

    .brand{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:14px;
      font-weight:900;
      letter-spacing:.2px;
    }

    .logo{
      width:44px;
      height:44px;
      border-radius:14px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(108,140,255,.22), rgba(44,229,192,.18)),
        #0d1730;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.35);
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    .logo::before{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      inset:0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(135deg, transparent 0 40%, rgba(255,255,255,.09) 50%, transparent 60% 100%);
      opacity:.7;
    }

    .logo span{
      position:relative;
      font-size:1rem;
      font-weight:900;
      color:#fff;
    }

    .brand-text{
      display:flex;
      flex-direction:column;
      line-height:1.05;
    }

    .brand-text strong{
      font-size:1rem;
    }

    .brand-text small{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:.72rem;
      font-weight:700;
      letter-spacing:.3px;
    }

    .nav-links{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:24px;
      font-weight:700;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .nav-links a:hover{
      color:#fff;
    }

    .nav-actions{
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      gap:12px;
    }

    .menu-btn{
      display:none;
      background:none;
      border:none;
      color:#fff;
      font-size:1.8rem;
      cursor:pointer;
    }

    .hero{
      padding:86px 0 64px;
      position:relative;
    }

    .hero-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1.12fr .88fr;
      gap:36px;
      align-items:center;
    }

    .hero h1{
      font-size:clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 5rem);
      line-height:1.02;
      letter-spacing:-2px;
      margin-bottom:18px;
      max-width:760px;
    }

    .gradient-text{
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #98b0ff 45%, #69f1d8 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip:text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;
      background-clip:text;
      color:transparent;
    }

    .hero p{
      max-width:650px;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:1.06rem;
      margin-bottom:28px;
    }

    .hero-actions{
      display:flex;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      gap:12px;
      margin-bottom:26px;
    }

    .hero-proof{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap:14px;
    }

    .proof-card{
      padding:18px;
      border-radius:18px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .proof-card h3{
      font-size:1.65rem;
      line-height:1;
      margin-bottom:8px;
    }

    .proof-card p{
      margin:0;
      font-size:.93rem;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .hero-panel{
      border-radius:28px;
      padding:22px;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.06), rgba(255,255,255,.03));
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
      position:relative;
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    .hero-panel::after{
      content:"";
      position:absolute;
      width:260px;
      height:260px;
      right:-60px;
      bottom:-80px;
      background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(108,140,255,.3), transparent 65%);
      pointer-events:none;
    }

    .panel-top{
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:16px;
      align-items:flex-start;
      margin-bottom:16px;
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
    }

    .panel-top h3{
      font-size:1.15rem;
      margin-bottom:4px;
    }

    .panel-top p{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:.94rem;
      margin:0;
    }

    .status{
      padding:8px 12px;
      border-radius:999px;
      border:1px solid rgba(44,229,192,.22);
      background:rgba(44,229,192,.09);
      color:#8ef3de;
      font-size:.86rem;
      font-weight:800;
      white-space:nowrap;
    }

    .chart{
      height:190px;
      border-radius:18px;
      overflow:hidden;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(108,140,255,.16), transparent),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(255,255,255,.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
        #091224;
      background-size:auto, 42px 42px, 42px 42px, auto;
      position:relative;
      margin-bottom:16px;
      z-index:1;
    }

    .chart svg{
      position:absolute;
      inset:0;
      width:100%;
      height:100%;
    }

    .mini-grid{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
      gap:14px;
      position:relative;
      z-index:1;
    }

    .box{
      background:var(--card);
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:18px;
      padding:18px;
    }

    .box h4{
      font-size:.96rem;
      margin-bottom:8px;
    }

    .box .big{
      font-size:1.9rem;
      line-height:1;
      font-weight:900;
      letter-spacing:-1px;
      margin-bottom:6px;
    }

    .box .sub{
      font-size:.92rem;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .section-head{
      max-width:760px;
      margin-bottom:34px;
    }

    .section-head h2{
      font-size:clamp(1.9rem, 3.2vw, 3.1rem);
      line-height:1.08;
      letter-spacing:-1.2px;
      margin-bottom:12px;
    }

    .section-head p{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:1.03rem;
    }

    .grid-3{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap:20px;
    }

    .card{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.05), rgba(255,255,255,.025));
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:22px;
      padding:24px;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .card-icon{
      width:54px;
      height:54px;
      border-radius:16px;
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      font-size:1.35rem;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(108,140,255,.18), rgba(44,229,192,.16));
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      margin-bottom:16px;
    }

    .card h3{
      font-size:1.18rem;
      margin-bottom:10px;
    }

    .card p{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:.98rem;
    }

    .split{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
      gap:22px;
    }

    .stack{
      display:grid;
      gap:14px;
    }

    .feature{
      display:flex;
      gap:14px;
      align-items:flex-start;
      padding:16px;
      border-radius:18px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);
      border:1px solid var(--line);
    }

    .feature-num{
      width:42px;
      height:42px;
      border-radius:12px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(108,140,255,.24), rgba(44,229,192,.18));
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      font-size:.95rem;
      font-weight:900;
      flex:0 0 42px;
    }

    .feature strong{
      display:block;
      margin-bottom:4px;
      font-size:1rem;
    }

    .feature span{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:.95rem;
    }

    .pricing{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap:20px;
    }

    .price-card{
      position:relative;
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.05), rgba(255,255,255,.025));
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:24px;
      padding:28px;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .price-card.featured{
      transform:translateY(-4px);
      border-color:rgba(108,140,255,.5);
      box-shadow:0 24px 80px rgba(108,140,255,.16);
    }

    .badge{
      position:absolute;
      top:18px;
      right:18px;
      padding:8px 12px;
      border-radius:999px;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--primary-2));
      color:#07111f;
      font-size:.8rem;
      font-weight:900;
    }

    .price-card h3{
      font-size:1.18rem;
      margin-bottom:8px;
    }

    .price{
      font-size:2.45rem;
      line-height:1;
      font-weight:900;
      letter-spacing:-1px;
      margin:10px 0 6px;
    }

    .price small{
      font-size:1rem;
      color:var(--muted);
      font-weight:700;
    }

    .price-desc{
      color:var(--muted);
      margin-bottom:18px;
    }

    .price-card ul{
      list-style:none;
      display:grid;
      gap:12px;
      margin:22px 0;
    }

    .price-card li{
      color:#dbe5ff;
      font-size:.98rem;
    }

    .price-card li::before{
      content:"✓";
      color:var(--primary-2);
      font-weight:900;
      margin-right:10px;
    }

    .cta{
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:20px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      align-items:center;
      padding:36px;
      border-radius:28px;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(108,140,255,.15), transparent 32%),
        radial-gradient(circle at bottom right, rgba(44,229,192,.10), transparent 28%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.05), rgba(255,255,255,.025));
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .cta h2{
      font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3vw, 2.8rem);
      line-height:1.08;
      margin-bottom:10px;
      letter-spacing:-1px;
    }

    .cta p{
      color:var(--muted);
      max-width:760px;
    }

    .faq{
      display:grid;
      gap:14px;
    }

    .faq-item{
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:18px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);
      overflow:hidden;
    }

    .faq-question{
      width:100%;
      background:none;
      border:none;
      color:#fff;
      text-align:left;
      padding:18px 20px;
      cursor:pointer;
      display:flex;
      align-items:center;
      justify-content:space-between;
      gap:16px;
      font-size:1rem;
      font-weight:800;
    }

    .faq-answer{
      display:none;
      padding:0 20px 18px;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .faq-item.active .faq-answer{
      display:block;
    }

    .contact{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
      gap:24px;
    }

    .contact-card{
      background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.05), rgba(255,255,255,.025));
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius:24px;
      padding:24px;
      box-shadow:var(--shadow);
    }

    .contact-list{
      display:grid;
      gap:14px;
      margin-top:18px;
    }

    .contact-item{
      display:flex;
      gap:14px;
      align-items:flex-start;
      padding:16px;
      border-radius:18px;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);
    }

    .contact-item strong{
      display:block;
      margin-bottom:4px;
    }

    .contact-item span{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:.95rem;
    }

    .form{
      display:grid;
      gap:14px;
      margin-top:16px;
    }

    .form-row{
      display:grid;
      grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
      gap:14px;
    }

    .form input,
    .form textarea,
    .form select{
      width:100%;
      background:#091224;
      border:1px solid var(--line);
      color:#fff;
      padding:14px 16px;
      border-radius:14px;
      outline:none;
      font:inherit;
    }

    .form input:focus,
    .form textarea:focus,
    .form select:focus{
      border-color:rgba(108,140,255,.7);
      box-shadow:0 0 0 4px rgba(108,140,255,.12);
    }

    .form textarea{
      resize:vertical;
      min-height:130px;
    }

    .form-note{
      color:var(--muted);
      font-size:.9rem;
      margin-top:2px;
    }

    .form-status{
      display:none;
      margin-top:8px;
      padding:12px 14px;
      border-radius:12px;
      font-weight:700;
      font-size:.94rem;
    }

    .form-status.success{
      display:block;
      background:rgba(22,197,95,.12);
      color:#9df0bf;
      border:1px solid rgba(22,197,95,.2);
    }

    .form-status.error{
      display:block;
      background:rgba(255,107,129,.12);
      color:#ffb8c5;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,107,129,.2);
    }

    .socials{
      display:flex;
      gap:12px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
      margin-top:18px;
    }

    footer{
      padding:24px 0 42px;
      color:var(--muted);
    }

    .footer{
      padding-top:24px;
      border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
      display:flex;
      justify-content:space-between;
      align-items:center;
      gap:20px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    .footer-links{
      display:flex;
      gap:18px;
      flex-wrap:wrap;
    }

    .footer-links a:hover{
      color:#fff;
    }

    .whatsapp-float{
      position:fixed;
      right:18px;
      bottom:18px;
      z-index:120;
      width:60px;
      height:60px;
      border-radius:999px;
      display:grid;
      place-items:center;
      background:linear-gradient(135deg, #1bd267, #08a64f);
      color:#fff;
      box-shadow:0 18px 40px rgba(10,166,79,.35);
      font-size:1.6rem;
    }

    .whatsapp-float:hover{
      transform:translateY(-2px);
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px){
      .hero-grid,
      .split,
      .pricing,
      .grid-3,
      .contact{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .hero-proof{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 880px){
      .nav-links,
      .nav-actions{
        display:none;
      }

      .menu-btn{
        display:block;
      }

      .mobile-menu{
        display:none;
        padding:0 0 18px;
      }

      .mobile-menu.active{
        display:grid;
        gap:10px;
      }

      .mobile-menu a{
        padding:14px 16px;
        border:1px solid var(--line);
        border-radius:14px;
        background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);
        font-weight:700;
      }
    }

    @media (min-width: 881px){
      .mobile-menu{
        display:none !important;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px){
      .hero{
        padding-top:64px;
      }

      .hero h1{
        letter-spacing:-1.4px;
      }

      .form-row{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .mini-grid{
        grid-template-columns:1fr;
      }

      .cta{
        padding:28px;
      }

      .section{
        padding:70px 0;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!--
    IMPORTANTE:
    1) Troque o número do WhatsApp em todos os links wa.me abaixo.
    2) Para o formulário funcionar de verdade, este arquivo já está ligado ao FormSubmit.
    3) Você precisa trocar SEUEMAIL@EXEMPLO.COM pelo seu e-mail real nas linhas do formulário.
  -->

  <header>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="nav">
        <a href="#home" class="brand" aria-label="NOXAR">
          <div class="logo"><span>N</span></div>
          <div class="brand-text">
            <strong>NOXAR</strong>
            <small>INTELIGÊNCIA OPERACIONAL</small>
          </div>
        </a>

        <nav class="nav-links">
          <a href="#solucoes">Soluções</a>
          <a href="#como-funciona">Como funciona</a>
          <a href="#planos">Planos</a>
          <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
          <a href="#contato">Contato</a>
        </nav>

        <div class="nav-actions">
          <a
            class="btn btn-secondary"
            href="https://wa.me/5511999999999?text=Ol%C3%A1%2C%20quero%20entender%20como%20a%20NOXAR%20pode%20automatizar%20minha%20empresa."
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
          >WhatsApp</a>
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contato">Agendar diagnóstico</a>
        </div>

        <button class="menu-btn" id="menuBtn" aria-label="Abrir menu">☰</button>
      </div>

      <div class="mobile-menu" id="mobileMenu">
        <a href="#solucoes">Soluções</a>
        <a href="#como-funciona">Como funciona</a>
        <a href="#planos">Planos</a>
        <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
        <a href="#contato">Contato</a>
        <a
          href="https://wa.me/5511999999999?text=Ol%C3%A1%2C%20quero%20entender%20como%20a%20NOXAR%20pode%20automatizar%20minha%20empresa."
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="btn btn-whatsapp"
        >Falar no WhatsApp</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero" id="home">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">
            <span class="eyebrow-dot"></span>
            IA, automação e sistemas para crescimento sem atrito
          </div>

          <h1>
            Empresas comuns contratam mais gente.
            <span class="gradient-text">Empresas ambiciosas constroem sistemas.</span>
          </h1>

          <p>
            A NOXAR cria infraestrutura digital para empresas que querem escalar com velocidade,
            margem e previsibilidade. Substituímos processos manuais por IA, automação e dados.
